Class UnchangeableSettingsHandler

java.lang.Object
org.xml.sax.helpers.DefaultHandler
blackjack.UnchangeableSettingsHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
ContentHandler, DTDHandler, EntityResolver, ErrorHandler
public class UnchangeableSettingsHandler extends DefaultHandler
SAX handler to parse the game settings XML file and initialize the game constants in UnchangeableSettings.
